## VMConfig.redirectTCPPorts property

List of TCP port numbers in the virtual machine that should be accessible from the host. For each redirection requested in this array, a [PortRedirection](./vm-providers.portredirection.md) object will be available in the [VM.tcpRedirections](./vm-providers.vm.tcpredirections.md) array.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
redirectTCPPorts?: number[];
```
